'''Meff''' is a derogatory term used in north-west [[England]], especially [[Liverpool]]. It is derived from the practice of hardened alcoholics drinking [[methylated spirits]] as they are untaxed and therefore cheaper.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://lingomash.com/slang-meanings/44044/slang-meaning-of-meff |title=What is the meaning of meff, what is the slang definition of meff, meff is slang for |publisher=Lingomash.com |date= |accessdate=2016-12-01}}</ref>


